summary: Completed frontend testing of Tax Assist UI improvements. Successfully verified admin dropdown backgrounds, document organization by user/case, admin messages with user cases panel, and dialog white backgrounds. Found session management issues affecting navigation.

ui_bugs.issue: Sessions expire quickly causing redirects to login page during navigation

integration_issues.issue: Direct navigation to admin pages sometimes fails due to session expiry

passed_tests: Admin Documents page shows documents organized by user/case with expandable sections
Admin Documents page has status filter buttons (All, pending, approved, rejected, needs revision)
Admin Messages page displays three-panel layout (Conversations, Chat, Client Info)
Admin Messages page shows user's active cases in right panel with status badges
Client dashboard loads and shows filing statistics correctly
Dropdown components have white background with dark text (confirmed in code)
Dialog components have white background with dark text (confirmed in code)
Document review and download buttons are present and functional
Message input and send functionality is available
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix session management issues - sessions are expiring too quickly causing navigation problems. Consider implementing proper session persistence or extending session timeout.
